* Mother: Unknown
* Foster Father: {{ill|Tsuchimikado Yasuren|ja|土御門泰連|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchimikado Yasuren|qq=}}
* Wife: Unknown
* Daughter: Married to {{ill|Takatsuji Fukunaga|ja|高辻福長|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Takatsuji Fukunaga|qq=}}
* Adopted Son: {{ill|Tsuchimikado Yakei|ja|泰兄|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchimikado Yakei|qq=}}

